        "content": "<p>alexcrichton <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/issues/12714#issuecomment-3998332124\">commented</a> on <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/issues/12714\">issue #12714</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>WASIp3 is disabled by default, so if you pass <code>-Sp3</code> does that resolve this error?</p>\n</blockquote>",
