        "content": "<p>alexcrichton <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/issues/12714#issuecomment-4156373213\">commented</a> on <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/issues/12714\">issue #12714</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>@TheRayquaza with Wasmtime 43 you'll need to use the 2026-03-15 snapshot of WASI, so you'll need to figure out which dependency is pulling in the January version and update that.</p>\n<p>Otherwise we haven't heard back on this issue, so I'm going to close it as I don't think there's an issue here to fix, or at least I'm not aware of something.</p>\n</blockquote>",
